              <div class="media-left text-primary">
                <i class="iconify" data-icon="ph:receipt-duotone"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="media-content">
                <h3 class="text-rainbow">Form controls</h3>
                <p>
                  Minimal offers a lot of prebuilt form controls. You can easily
